org.dessertj.slicing

Class ConcreteSlice

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dessertj.slicing.AbstractSlice
      • org.dessertj.slicing.ConcreteSlice
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Slice
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PartitionSlice

    public class ConcreteSlice
extends AbstractSlice
    A concrete slice is a concrete collection of classes. Hence, it contains a set of Clazz. The sum or difference on concrete slices produce a concrete slice again.
